Class ClosedCollection<E>

java.lang.Object
craterdog.smart.SmartObject<Sequence<E>>

craterdog.collections.abstractions.ClosedCollection<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of element managed by this collection.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Composite<Sequence<E>>, Sequential<E>, Comparable<Sequence<E>>, Iterable<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Queue, Stack
public abstract class ClosedCollection<E> extends Collection<E>
This abstract class implements a collection that does not allow its internal structure to be directly manipulated.
Author:
Derk Norton
